This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=3938

Trailer Trash highlights trailing white space to be teh same highlight as "ErrorMsg," making if very obvious.

It is smart enough no to highlight while you are typing, only when you exit insert will the whitespace be highlighted.

The source is on github here: https://github.com/csexton/trailertrash.vim
